evals/results/raw/
evals/results/*.json

# GauntletAI project notes (local only — mirrored to OneDrive backup,
# not for upstream). Anchored to repo root.
/.gauntlet/

# Claude Code session state (local only — mirrored to OneDrive backup).
/.claude/

# Working files at repo root that have repeatedly been swept in by
# `git add -A` despite living outside .gauntlet/. Pin them here so
# `git status` keeps them as ignored, not untracked.
/CLAUDE_SESSION_HANDOFF.md
